Interface FloatStack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Stack<java.lang.Float>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFloatBigList, AbstractFloatBigList.FloatSubList, AbstractFloatList, AbstractFloatList.FloatSubList, AbstractFloatStack, FloatArrayList, FloatBigArrayBigList, FloatBigLists.ListBigList, FloatBigLists.Singleton, FloatLists.Singleton

    public interface FloatStack
extends Stack<java.lang.Float>
    A type-specific Stack; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
